data.description: There are not many houses available under 500k in Fort Collins! Excellent location in Fort Collins close to Front Range Community College and Horsetooth Reservoir! This home features a bright open floor plan with vaulted ceilings that creates a welcoming atmosphere. Gorgeous remodeled kitchen with white cabinets, granite countertops, beautiful backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Off the kitchen area is the large wood deck area perfect for entertaining or enjoying your morning coffee. This home's versatile Bi-Level Layout offers a practical design, creating distinct living areas on both levels. Established apple tree, pear tree and grape vine that produce fruit every year. Fenced in yard with storage shed included. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, the home is close to schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transit routes. Make an investment in this thriving Fort Collins Real Estate market. We are available 7 days a week for private tours!
